**USE**: `Menu` from `@webpack/common/menu`

**Available components:**
- `Menu.Menu` - Main menu component
- `Menu.MenuItem` - Menu item
- `Menu.MenuCheckboxItem` - Checkbox menu item
- `Menu.MenuRadioItem` - Radio menu item
- `Menu.MenuSliderControl` - Slider control
- `Menu.MenuSearchControl` - Search control
- `ContextMenuApi` - Context menu API

**DO NOT**: Find menu components manually

```typescript
import { Menu, ContextMenuApi } from "@webpack/common";

<Menu.Menu>
    <Menu.MenuItem
        id="my-item"
        label="My Item"
        action={() => console.log("Clicked")}
